#N canvas 50 50 1280 1030 10;
#X text 30 15 MockMidterm.pd v2 - NES Sound Chip Emulation;
#X text 30 40 CMPM 125 Mock Midterm | Devin + partner | Pure Data + OSC from Unity;
#X text 30 75 INSTRUCTIONS:;
#X text 30 100 1) Click the DSP toggle below to enable audio.;
#X text 30 125 2) Open BallDemo_MockMidterm in Unity and press Play - or use the TEST PANEL on the right.;
#X text 30 150 3) Unity sends OSC to 127.0.0.1:8000 (UDP \, vanilla netreceive - no mrpeach dependency).;
#X text 30 175 4) Voices listen on internal buses [r osctrig] / [r oscwall] / [r osctempo] / [r oscplayseq].;
#X text 30 200 5) Adjust per-voice volume \, voice parameters \, and master to mix in real-time.;
#X obj 30 235 tgl 15 0 empty empty empty 17 7 0 10 -262144 -1 -1 0 1;
#X msg 30 265 \; pd dsp \$1;
