#X text 30 830 NOTES:;
#X text 30 858 - Each voice listens internally via [r osctrig] / [r oscwall] / [r osctempo] / [r oscplayseq].;
#X text 30 886 - VOICE PARAMETERS sliders use [hsl] SEND-NAME to talk to voice abstractions' control buses.;
#X text 30 914 - All voices use [vline~] -> [*~] envelopes for click-free attack/release (assignment requirement).;
#X text 30 942 - Per-voice + master volume use [hsl] -> [pack f 20] -> [line~] -> [*~] (20ms ramp).;
#X text 30 970 - Voice volume sliders start at 0 - raise them after enabling DSP.;
#X text 30 998 - Sequencer voice silent until partner adds [outlet~] to sequencer.pd.;
